                            <h2>VentureCrowd CEO Steve Maarbani spoke to Ticker INVEST about how Australia could become a global technology hub.</h2>
                            <p>
                                <span style="font-weight: 400;">Steve discusses the latest news in the Medtech sector with Adrian. </span>
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <span style="font-weight: 400;">He talks about the recent success of the VentureCrowd portfolio company 4DMedical. They talk about the success of the healthcare supply chain in Australia and the current Pre-IPO offer that VentureCrowd is currently investing in 
                                    <a href="https://vc-internal.force.com/s/blog/pre-ipo-investing-curae-health">Curae Health</a>. An exciting space in digitisation in the Dental space. 
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <strong>
                                    Watch the recording of the interview below.</strong>
